##Creating a Menu
1. Click on the Menus sub tab under Appearance.

    ![Appearance > Menu]({{ images }}Menu-Menu-Tab.png)

2. Select the menu to edit.

    ![Select a Menu]({{ images }}Menu-Select-Menu.png)

3. Select a Page to add to the menu
- Then click add to menu

    ![Select a Page]({{ images }}Menu-Select-Page.png)

3. Reorder Menu by dragging items in the list.

    ![Reorder Page]({{ images }}Menu-Reorder.png)

5. Save menu

    ![Save Menu]({{ images }}Menu-Save.png)